This test bucket contains unit tests for derived types with the BIND(C)
attribute.

bddiag*
These are diagnostic tests involving bad syntax, as well as having components
of all types (both interoperable and non-interoperable) in BIND(C) derived
types.

bdfunc01*
These tests involve passing an object of a BIND(C) derived type to a C 
routine, both by reference and by value, and using various lignment options.

bdfunc02*
These tests involve passing an object of a BIND(C) derived type to a Fortran
routine, both by reference and by value, and using various alignment options.
